<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīsakavarusaṁbulu 1377 Agu nēṭi
<lb n="2"/>bhādrapada sudha tritīĀ sanivarana <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīraśrī
<lb n="3" break="no"/>gajapati gaŪḍēsvara pratapakapiḷēsvara
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dēvaṁkara vijayarajyasamastha 25 srāhi ka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḷiṁgaparōkṣa śrīkuṁḍḍaḷēsvaramahāpātra
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ni Adhikarana <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> bhōgaparīkṣa ceṁgamanathani A
<lb n="7" break="no"/>diṭṭānamaṁdu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kuṁḍaḷēsvaramahāpatruni
<lb n="8"/>Āyusyakāmarthamu sidhigānu śrīkurmanā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>thuniki <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pratidinamu pavitramulāgi A
<lb n="10" break="no"/>Inaṭugānu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kaŪsikagōtruṁḍu ĀIna
<lb n="11"/>valabhayyagāriki <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> puruvaddatthamu khi
<lb n="12" break="no"/>la<unclear>mai</unclear>nadi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ūdhariṁpi <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> pōtamaribaṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>dhalōnu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> puṭeṁḍu kṣētramu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> prasada
<lb n="14" break="no"/>mu tumuṁḍū <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ācaṁdrārkkastāhigā Ū
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṁḍagaladu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> I dattamu tirupati
<lb n="16"/>śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattaṁ paradatta
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṁ va Ē harētu vasuṁdharī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śasthivarṣasaha
<lb n="18" break="no"/>sraṇi viṣṭayā jāyatē krimi <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśrīśrī
</p>

